title: Beyonce pregnancy photo series mirror classic paintings | Daily Mail Online
text: Beyonce the work of art: Queen Bey's pregnancy photo series echoes famous paintings featuring Venus and the Virgin Mary Beyonce shared a series of photos Thursday following her twin pregnancy news The pictures show her naked or in lingerie showcasing her new baby bump Mirror classic works of art such as Sandro Botticelli’s The Birth of Venus One photo with Blue Ivy calls to mind Guido Reni’s Reclining Venus With Cupid Her main Instagram snap was also compared to various Virgin Mary paintings
